### Notes
- WP admin login URL is `https://api.michaelwegter.com/wp-admin/` (no slug prefix — WP siteurl is set to the root, bridge rewrites correctly)
- Bridge redirect fix (commit 5210c3a) is working: login 302 cookies pass through correctly to browser
- CORS `allow-origin: http://localhost:3000` on WP responses is benign for iframe use; no JS cross-origin fetches from michaelwegter.com to the bridge
- `demo_admin` not tested (noted as stale hash in prior build); `mdr_admin` / `MDR_Restore_2026!` is the advertised credential
- Design palette confirmed via direct CSS fetch: `--charcoal-deep: #1A1D1A`, `--green-forest: #2F5D3A`, comment "Mobile-first. Deep charcoal, white, forest green. Playfair Display + Inter."

---

## handoff
- produced: Full Playwright live test (36 checks, 36 PASS); portfolio frame, iframe, all 8 WP pages, FAQ/gallery/form interactivity, WP admin login, Rank Math + Fluent Forms, api health all verified.
- decisions: CSS palette check is confirmed pass via direct CSS fetch (external stylesheet, not inline); no actual failures.
- next needs: media-capture — record hero flow (before/after slider, sticky CTAs, gallery lightbox, FAQ accordion).
- risks: `demo_admin` password may need reset if client wants dual-role demo; Docker container is single point of failure (auto-restart via services.json, but a Surface reboot adds ~10s lag); CORS origin shows localhost (harmless for iframe, matters only if future JS makes cross-origin fetch from michaelwegter.com).

VERDICT: pass
